{"tid":87916,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普上任象徵「新學期」 日漫畫精準呈現國際局勢！(圖)","createTime":"2017-01-20T08:03:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-20T11:33:52.000Z","uid":35790,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e94a96338e1e9240a5d19fd4bfbce063dd633255","tid":87916,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T08:03:39.000Z","msg":"川普上任象徵「新學期」 日漫畫精準呈現國際局勢！<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpo28EG0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpo28EG0.jpg&h=bb8176b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本漫畫家畫出國際局勢，獲得網友好評。（圖擷自東京新聞（中日新聞）政治部twitter）<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國準總統川普將上任，國際局勢可能因此改變，日本漫畫家佐藤正明日前發表諷刺插畫，把川普上任取名為「這個新學期」，精準畫出當前國際局勢，總統蔡英文也成為插畫角色。<br />\n<br />\n佐藤正明日前在《中日新聞》發表諷刺插畫，把場景設定在教室內，各國領導人都換上學校制服，並把插畫取名為「這個新學期」，用學校凸顯川普上任後的國際局勢，獲得網友好評。<br />\n<br />\n插畫中川普儼然是班上的老大，他坐在教室最中間與中國國家主席習近平激動對嗆，菲律賓總統杜特蒂則翹腳一臉不屑，看起來頗有狂人風範。<br />\n<br />\n蔡英文與日本首相安倍晉三則坐在最前排，兩人都愁容滿面，當中蔡英文還被習近平的紙團砸中，顯示兩岸關係不穩定；坐在後排的北韓領導人金正恩則射出紙飛機，還差點射中安倍。<br />\n<br />\n插畫也凸顯歐洲局勢，德國總理梅克爾、法國總統歐蘭德和英國首相梅伊3人形成班上的小團體；俄羅斯總統普丁與敘利亞總統阿塞德則成為班上異類，站在窗邊討論事情。<br />\n<br />\n此外，插畫也畫出南韓總統朴槿惠，但只被秀出小頭像，暗示被彈劾的她可能已轉學或遭退學。<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/1953574\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F1953574&d=OwLvdmaINEXasGCo93XTIgv3KisNQlPySkJrDkY9tT8%3D&h=68995e70\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F1953574&h=62684d43\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/1953574</a>"},{"pid":"8a846881ed2fefd86b3f9f5dfb1b2a395dd0a217","tid":87916,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T08:05:08.000Z","msg":"邊個係度玩紙飛機？"},{"pid":"a314ca21fb52239085d8b9e6eb2089160dba2ea9","tid":87916,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T08:06:23.000Z","msg":"金正恩<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBtw好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee04c19c30e6e1267013b8b886c52803ab19be54","tid":87916,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T08:06:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊個係度玩紙飛機？</blockquote><br />\n&gt;坐在後排的北韓領導人金正恩則射出紙飛機，還差點射中安倍。"},{"pid":"17f2bd73eefe2e767e6f7bca713f547d983d0894","tid":87916,"uid":53775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T08:06:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊個係度玩紙飛機？</blockquote><br />\n金仔"},{"pid":"8b3ade2d708a9b6f1f64c4961f00c15ef5358fbf","tid":87916,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T08:08:05.000Z","msg":"畫到普京成個隱藏大佬咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf3087ec37281a00dea2eafac3f29650be2ebba5","tid":87916,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T08:08:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊個係度玩紙飛機？</blockquote><br />\n一隻字都無睇下？"},{"pid":"9570b860bad64bad3278b3b9aef814515eb1ff2b","tid":87916,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T08:10:08.000Z","msg":"諗起歷史科d漫畫題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90fd5d147fecd090a61a40048e79aba7c3b1b0d1","tid":87916,"uid":22566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T08:10:33.000Z","msg":"後面貼堂個啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e176f51f9476278f38d5ef5a9734204c8d620de7","tid":87916,"uid":2265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T08:12:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0a1d30c2de0bed8f84d7e2ab0846a6f5eb982b5","tid":87916,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T08:13:13.000Z","msg":"警告你！ 唔好再擲前面四眼妹！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hk